  "detailed_description": "<h1>UPCOMING GAMES</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/d568d1f282abc9a20f59ca1486e25f4c.poster.avif?t=1733330068\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/d568d1f282abc9a20f59ca1486e25f4c.webm?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/d568d1f282abc9a20f59ca1486e25f4c.mp4?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>GAME</strong><br>Follow The Cat is a first-person puzzle game based on manipulating shape and physics of \"Magnetic Cube\". You make your path with using special glove through story with mysterious cat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/c7f477d0ded47c8d4c5049ce95f8ee7f.poster.avif?t=1733330068\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/c7f477d0ded47c8d4c5049ce95f8ee7f.webm?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/c7f477d0ded47c8d4c5049ce95f8ee7f.mp4?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>STORY</strong><br>In the extraordinary evaluation process of the company to hire new employees. An unexpected guest will accompany you. Experience an unusual job interview method and unravel the mystery of the guest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/591bb0d50ce052c6d57f452a4f9f90dc.poster.avif?t=1733330068\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/591bb0d50ce052c6d57f452a4f9f90dc.webm?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/591bb0d50ce052c6d57f452a4f9f90dc.mp4?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DESIGN</strong><br>Visually designed spaces to enrich experience  and story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/f4850216c4d3764d341f7345cd6302f3.poster.avif?t=1733330068\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/f4850216c4d3764d341f7345cd6302f3.webm?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1725480/extras/f4850216c4d3764d341f7345cd6302f3.mp4?t=1733330068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
